{"type":"message","id":"c0a1d0ba","parentId":"f236a9e6","timestamp":"2026-04-01T02:03:08.401Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if they can talk to me on WeChat and ask me to operate/manage Feishu (Lark) spreadsheets. This is a question about whether the current setup supports cross-platform operations - specifically, using WeChat as the interface to control Feishu bitable/sheet operations.\n\nBased on the context:\n- Channel is openclaw-weixin (WeChat)\n- Feishu integration is already configured (we saw feishu tools available)\n- The user has already completed Feishu authorization\n\nThe answer should be yes - the system already has both WeChat and Feishu integrations working. The user can indeed send commands via WeChat to operate Feishu bitables, calendars, docs, etc. The tools are all available in this session.\n\nLet me confirm this for the user.","thinkingSignature":"43a2033f2c2eedb51090229aefa89d61a73fb24a1f0737a6942546893a3bd4a5"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n完全可以！\n\n你的系统同时接入了微信和飞书，而且你已经完成了飞书授权。所以你完全可以在微信上跟我说话，我来帮你操作飞书的云文档、云表格、日历、消息等。\n\n比如你可以说：\n- \"帮我看看飞书上有哪些多维表格\"\n- \"在飞书云表格里新增一条记录\"\n- \"查一下飞书日历里今天的会议\"\n\n我都能帮你搞定。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107,"output":259,"cacheRead":34244,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34610,"cost":{"input":0.0000321,"output":0.00031079999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00205464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00239754}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775008977461,"responseId":"061bafd2b4315503864ec6f3652ace25"}}
